追加分②｜Carestream Health 特許概要
知財：Carestream Health の特許概要
A method for diagnosing diseases by inspecting images of an individual's tongue comprising:

・forming a first image of said tongue, a color checker, and a portion of said individual's face;
・forming a second image of said tongue and said portion of said individual's face;
・performing a color comparison of said portion of said individual's face in said second image to said portion of said individual's face in said first image;
・matching the colors in said second image to the colors in said first image based on said color comparison; and
・diagnosing at least one disease based on said color comparison.

要点（日本語要約）
・舌＋顔の一部を含めて撮影
・色補正（カラーチェッカー）を行う
・顔色を基準に舌色を補正
・色の変化から疾病を診断

補足（資料内日本語）
Carestream Healthの特許は、
舌＋顔の一部を参照して色調補正を行う点が特徴。
顔の一部を参照しなければ権利範囲外。

